upcomingEvents.name: ACSL Contest #1
upcomingEvents.desc:
ACSL's first programming competition. Includes both short-answer and programming sections.

Topics: Computer Number Systems, Recursive Functions, What Does This Program Do?

For more details about the competition or to study, please refer to the ACSL tab.
For more information on the deadlines for the two sections, check the Deadlines section a week or two in advance.

upcomingEvents.name: ACSL Contest #2
upcomingEvents.desc:
ACSL's second programming competition. Includes both short-answer and programming sections.

Topics: Prefix/Infix/Postfix Notation, Bit-String Flicking, LISP

For more details about the competition or to study, please refer to the ACSL tab.
For more information on the deadlines for the two sections, check the Deadlines section a week or two in advance.

upcomingEvents.name: ACSL Contest #3
upcomingEvents.desc:
ACSL's third programming competition. Includes both short-answer and programming sections.

For more details about the competition or to study, please refer to the ACSL tab.
For more information on the deadlines for the two sections, check the Deadlines section a week or two in advance.

upcomingEvents.name: ACSL Contest #4
upcomingEvents.desc:
ACSL's fourth and final programming competition. Includes both short-answer and programming sections.

Topics: Graph Theory, Digital Electronics, Assembly Language

For more details about the competition or to study, please refer to the ACSL tab.
